[section Singleton]

A quick singleton implementation might look as follows:

 Single::Single() : impl_ptr_type(null())
 {
     static Single single = Single::null();
     static bool   inited = (single.emplace<implementation>(...), true);

     *this = single; // All point to the same implementation.
 }

All instances of ['Single] share the same implementation.

[endsect]
